{"tid":194630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"從星加坡遭貶稱 little red dot 到台灣柯文哲嘲笑所有鄰國","createTime":"2017-04-10T06:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T08:01:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c64ac81c47332fe196b51417802043289cbc3073","tid":194630,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.fcbc.org.sg/sites/default/files/happyjubilee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fcbc.org.sg%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fhappyjubilee.jpg&h=5e3b622c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n星加坡以前被印尼笑係 little red dot<br />\n於是星加坡人就話自己係 little red dot, 仲做埋brand<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.static-economist.com/sites/default/files/imagecache/1872-width/images/print-edition/20150718_SRP009_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.static-economist.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fimagecache%2F1872-width%2Fimages%2Fprint-edition%2F20150718_SRP009_0.jpg&h=3cc3c533&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後1998年, 印尼盾被索羅斯狙擊, 大幅貶值, 直接累死埋香港本土投資銀行百富勤既印尼的士企業債<br />\n<br />\n星加坡財金官員話, 我地只係 little red dot<br />\n所以無能力幫到你地印尼對應亞洲金融風暴, sor9ry  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n柯文哲依家屌晒全部鄰國<br />\n我只見到台灣將來會死得好慘"},{"pid":"0db90428f1a7df9a8bb0ebe433acd4fdcdfdee42","tid":194630,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到時就港台友好，日台友好，星台友好......"},{"pid":"cb099a1ad746a0750ed15c3d77793083762c65d0","tid":194630,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:09:55.000Z","msg":"文呢？<br />\nBtw, 台狗自卑到周圍咬人，真係陰鳩公"},{"pid":"a4b9e106fbbc8753752d12495208a47d8651faba","tid":194630,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://eznewlife.com/focus_photos/2012_02_0442.jpg\" data-thum